7.8,, 127,, Drama, Romance,, Joe Wright,, Keira Knightley, Matthew Macfadyen, Brenda Blethyn, Donald Sutherland,, Sparks fly when spirited Elizabeth Bennett meets single, rich, and proud Mr. Darcy. But Mr. Darcy reluctantly finds himself falling in love with a woman beneath his class. Can each overcome their own pride and prejudice?